iweather station, log on to the school network, and then disconnect.		{{server_addr}}	{{server_port}}
iThe device will not be kicked out from logged-on status during short		{{server_addr}}	{{server_port}}
idisconnections, and when the weather station is powered on at this		{{server_addr}}	{{server_port}}
itime, it will be able to connect to the Internet without logging on		{{server_addr}}	{{server_port}}
iitself.		{{server_addr}}	{{server_port}}
