i`INFLUXDB` with an extra tag `id=1` for device identification and a		{{server_addr}}	{{server_port}}
ivalue of 3.5. Actually, one request may contain multiple data points		{{server_addr}}	{{server_port}}
iseparated by Linux line feed `\n`. Note that you cannot use `\r\n`		{{server_addr}}	{{server_port}}
iinstead; this will cause an error.		{{server_addr}}	{{server_port}}
i		{{server_addr}}	{{server_port}}
iHere we have our code (simplified) to generate the HTTP request:		{{server_addr}}	{{server_port}}
